mall|date=16 September 2016|newspaper=The Tribune Lifestyle|accessdate=26 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\n\nDiljott is a trained actor from a Mumbai acting institute and is a [[Kathak]], western, and folk dancer. After working with photographer Dabboo Ratanani, she featured in advertisements for clothing brands and magazine covers including Hindustan Petroleum Corporation Limited, Larsen and Toubro. \n\nShe is fluent in English, [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]] and [[Hindi]] and works in [[Bollywood]] and Punjabi cinema as an actress.<ref>{{cite news|title= Plans for Pollywood |url= https://epaper.tribuneindia.com/c/35371424 |date= 1 January 2019|accessdate= 1 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nShe featured in the Punjabi song \"Patiala Peg\" opposite Diljit Dosanjh,<ref>{{cite news|title= Emerging Punjabi Actress |url= http://epaperbeta.timesofindia.com/Article.aspx?eid=31973&articlexml=EMERGING-PUNJABI-SIRENS-29102016107021|date= 29 October 2016|accessdate= 31 October 2016}}</ref> which became a hit track.<ref>{{cite news|title=Diljott: Meet The  \u2018Patiala Peg\u2019 Girl|url=http://www.darpanmagazine.com/magazine/spotlight/diljott-meet-the-patiala-peg-girl/|newspaper=Darpan Magazine|date=26 November 2015|accessdate=8 September 2016}}</ref> Diljott's films as a lead actress in ''Teshan''<ref>{{cite news|title= Film Teshan|url=https://dailypost.in/news/entertainment/set-big-screen-debut/|newspaper= Daily Post|date= 24 September 2016|accessdate=26 September 2016}}</ref> (2016)<ref>{{cite news|title= Teshan 2016 Movie|url=http://www.unp.me/f185/teshan-2016-happy-raikoti-and-diljott-movie-295258/|newspaper= Punjabi Internet Portal|date= 25 August 2016|accessdate=10 September 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= All set for the Big Screen|url=http://epaper.dailypostindia.com/epapermain.aspx?queryed=9&eddate=2016-09-23|newspaper= Daily Post|date= 23 September 2016|accessdate=23 September 2016}}</ref> and ''Yaar Annmulle 2'' (2017)<ref>{{cite news|title= Film Yaar Annmulle 2 |u