accessdate= 22 June 2016}}</ref> Another single was \"Akh Mataka\" (2017).<ref>{{cite news|title= Diljott's new single track song 'Akh Mataka'|url=https://www.gabruu.com/vekho-diljott-de-aaun-vale-gane-akh-mataka-de-behind-the-camera-scenes/|newspaper=Gabruu|date= 26 June 2017|accessdate= 27 June 2017}}</ref> Dilijott performed at the 2016 Virasat International Punjabi Film Festival and Awards.<ref>{{cite news|title=No one formula to success:Diljott|url=http://m.epaper.bhaskar.com/magazine/navrang-punjab/450/04082017/mpcg/2/|newspaper=Dainik Bhaskar|date= 3 August 2017|accessdate= 4 August 2017}}</ref> Her song \"Maa Meri\" (2017) is an ode to mothers. \"Just Love You\" (2018) was a romantic song.\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Film\n!scope=\"col\"| Language\n!scope=\"col\"| Role\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Teshan (film)|Teshan]]''\n| Punjabi language|Punjabi\n| Jinni\n| Film released on 23 September 2016. Directed by Sukhbir Singh, the film stars Happy Raikoti, Diljott, Yograj Singh, Karamjit Anmol, Shavinder Mahal, Anita Devgan, Prince Kanwaljit Singh, Nisha Bano and many more.\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Yaar Annmulle 2'' \n| Punjabi\n| Sabar\n| Film released on 6 January 2017. Directed by Sunny Mahal, the film stars Sarbjit Cheema, Sarthi K, Raja Baath, Diljott, Yograj Singh, Param Saini, Rana Jung Bahadur and many more.\n|-\n| 2018\n! scope=\"row\"| ''5 Weddings '' \n| English\n| Harleen\n| Hollywood film released in 2018 worldwide. The film stars Raj Kummar Rao, Nargis Fakhri, Diljott, Candy Clark, Bo Derek, Anneliese Der Pol, Mariana and many more.\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Khatre Da Ghuggu '' \n| Punjabi\n| Meet\n| A Punjabi film released worldwide on 17 January 2020. The film stars Jordan Sandhu, Diljott, BN Sharma and others.\n|-\n|}\n\n==Songs==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable so